title: Road Centerlines
description:
This layer contains a geospatial representation of the center of the paved surface of a travel roadway for all public and some private streets in Prince George's County, Maryland. Attributes for the centerline contain street information, routing functionality, and class type.  The line work was created from the 1993 1FT aerial imagery and the attributes were entered by CENTECH Inc. This layer is maintained by Prince George's County Office of Information Technology and is primarily used to support the emergency response 911 system as well as other functions for the County agencies.
